### Create user (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "alice", "password": "Test@1234" }

###

### Create user — duplicate username (expect 409)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "alice", "password": "Other@5678" }

###

### Create user — missing fields (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "", "password": "" }

###

### Get user (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/1

###

### Get user — not found (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/99999
